the states of Massachusetts, Maine, Vermont, New Hampshire, Connecticut
and Rhode Island).

CLIMATE: Warm and sunny from may to October, cold winters.

CLOTHING: Lightweight cotton in summer.

AIR TRAVEL: From Boston to London is 7 hours 15 minutes. Plus USA 
Internal domestic flights to all major cities.
