Minnesota gateway including Minneapolis/St Paul, gateway to the Great
lakes, the prairielands of Minnesota, Wisconsin and Iowa, and the great
plains and badlands of Nebraska. North Dakota and South Dakota.

CLIMATE: Winters are cold with severe conditions along the great lakes.
Summers are warm and there are frequent heat waves and droughts.

CLOTHING: Lighweight cotton clothing for summer, with sweaters and
jackets for winter.

AIR TRAVEL: Minneapolis-St Paul to London is 12 hours 45 minutes
(including stopover). Plus USA internal domestic flights to all major
cities.
