Missouri including St Louis and Kansas City, Gateways to south/central
USA - MIssouri, Kansas, Oklahoma and Arkansas.

CLIMATE: The region has the most continental climate of any area in the
USA. Winters are cold and summers warm, with frequent heat waves.

CLOTHING: Lighweight cotton clothing for summer, with sweaters and
jackets for winter.

AIR TRAVEL: St Louis to London is 9 hours 10 minutes (including stopover).
Kansas City to London is 13 hours 20 minutes (including stopover).
Plus USA internal domestic flights to all major cities.
@endnode

