Country - the States of Pennsylvania, Delaware, Maryland, West Virginia
and Virginia.

CLIMATE: The weather can be changeable, with moderate amounts of rain
throughout the year. Summers are warm with occasional heatwaves.

CLOTHING: Lightweights during the summer, heavyweights during the winter.

AIR TRAVEL: Philadelphia to London is 9 hours 25 minutes (including
stopover). Plus USA internal domestic flights to all major cities.
